      <description>&lt;div class="wi_fic_desc" property="description"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Himari married Alex for her money, but now that they're divorced and Himari is onto her next mark she still can't stop seeking the thrill she found in Alex.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Alex knew that Himari was her soulmate from the moment they met. She has been patient for the years after their divorce, waiting for Himari to come to her senses. But patience has its limits.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1337192-if-i-dont-know-it-wont-hurt/chapter/1337201/"&gt;&lt;div class="chapter-title"&gt;Alex&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="chp_raw" id="chp_raw"&gt;&lt;div class="wi_authornotes"&gt; &lt;div&gt; &lt;div class="p-avatar-wrap"&gt;&lt;a class="avatar has-link" href="/profile/19892/azura/"&gt;&lt;img id="acc_ava_change profile" alt="" src="https://cdn.scribblehub.com/avatar/s/4/ava_19892_1578802840.jpg"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="an_username"&gt;&lt;a href="/profile/19892/azura/"&gt;Azura&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div style="clear: both;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="wi_authornotes_body"&gt;  Hello lovelies! Something new and delightful here for you. A little darker, and (at least I think) the best thing I've ever written. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Some extensive (though not necessarily complete) content warnings&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="sp-wrap sp-wrap-default"&gt; &lt;div class="sp-head" title="Expand"&gt; Spoiler &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="sp-body folded"&gt; &lt;p&gt;Toxic/Abusive relationships. Obsessive Behavior, Reckless driving, Not wearing appropriate clothes for the weather, Sadism, Masochism, Degradation, Infidelity, Spousal abuse (a slap), Unplanned pregnancy. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;div class="spdiv"&gt;[collapse]&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Alex was getting ready for a date when the call came. When she saw her ex