      <title>The Intricate Art of Assassination</title>
      <author> TangledVirus </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1336583/the-intricate-art-of-assassination/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1336583-the-intricate-art-of-assassination/chapter/1336595/#comments</comments>
