      <title>I Wanted a Second Chance, But Not Like This</title>
      <author> valtarra </author>
      <link>https://www.scribblehub.com/series/1325679/i-wanted-a-second-chance-but-not-like-this/</link>
      <comments>https://www.scribblehub.com/read/1325679-i-wanted-a-second-chance-but-not-like-this/chapter/1325698/#comments</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">e2030a020a72c0c40e49cbf662fcca84cf2ca585</guid>
